      <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
         <note type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Batteries give off flammable fumes that can explode.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">Do not smoke when observing the battery electrolyte levels.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">Electrolyte is an acid and can cause personal injury if it contacts skin or eyes.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">Always wear protective glasses when working with batteries.</p>
